{"ID":"20260424101900-2ustd6z","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260424101900-2ustd6z","title":"04_数据流_硬件循环_片上存储","type":"doc","updated":"20260424101900"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101900-9wq0zuh","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101900-9wq0zuh","updated":"20260424101900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"04 数据流、硬件循环、片上存储"}]},{"ID":"20260424101900-i3ee2iz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101900-i3ee2iz","updated":"20260424101900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上一卷把计算核心拆到了 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"MAC / PE / 阵列 / 数据路径 / 精度 / 控制"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 六个维度。这一卷继续往下压，讨论真正决定可持续吞吐的部分："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"数据怎样复用"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​、"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"循环怎样展开"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​、"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"片上存储怎样分层"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​、"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"DMA 怎样把搬运和计算重叠起来"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101900-y52dfni","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101900-y52dfni","updated":"20260424101900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"同样规模的阵列，效率可以差很多，根源通常不在乘法器，而在这一整条链没有对齐。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101900-6xm52sn","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101900-6xm52sn","updated":"20260424101900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. 为什么这卷比“再加一点算力”更重要"}]},{"ID":"20260424101900-mmdtzes","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101900-mmdtzes","updated":"20260424101900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"神经网络工作负载里，阵列规模经常不是第一个瓶颈，原因有三个："}]},{"ID":"20260424101900-rh4qkk5","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101900-rh4qkk5","updated":"20260424101900"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101900-ko2vtww","Type":"NodeListItem","ListD